comment: /**  * Is the {@link SubUnitOfWork} marked as failed.  *  * @return <tt>true</tt> to indicate this sub unit of work is failed.  */
code: /**  * Is the {@link SubUnitOfWork} marked as failed.  *  * @return <tt>true</tt> to indicate this sub unit of work is failed.  */ boolean isFailed().

comment: /**  * If failed then a number of exceptions could have occurred, causing the {@link SubUnitOfWork} to fail.  *  * @return the caused exceptions.  */
code: /**  * If failed then a number of exceptions could have occurred, causing the {@link SubUnitOfWork} to fail.  *  * @return the caused exceptions.  */ List<Exception> getExceptions().
